data.eml:eml: Morphological redescription of the immature and adult stages of Culex (Culex) acharistus Root (Diptera: Culicidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Laurito, Magdalena, Almirón, Walter Ricardo, Rossi, Gustavo Carlos (2009): Morphological redescription of the immature and adult stages of Culex (Culex) acharistus Root (Diptera: Culicidae). Zootaxa 2263: 21-30, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.190769
